{"view":"article","slug":"visualcube-simplified-image-setting","category":"Tools","subcategory":null,"topDir":"Tools","title":{"en":"VisualCube Simplified Image Setting 简化图设置"},"content":{"en":"<p><strong>VisualCube Simplified Image Setting 简化图设置</strong></p><p><strong>特征</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/visualcube-simplified-image-setting/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/visualcube-simplified-image-setting/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/visualcube-simplified-image-setting/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>棒 (Bar)</p></td><td><p>反线 (Opp Line)</p></td><td><p>花灯 (CECE)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/visualcube-simplified-image-setting/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/visualcube-simplified-image-setting/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/visualcube-simplified-image-setting/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>灯 (Light)</p></td><td><p>反棒 (Opp bar)</p></td><td><p>花砖 (ECEC)</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>平面图简化</strong> (用于&amp;view=plan)</p><p>假设顶层中心为黄. 默认顶层黄格全保留. 然后在忽略黄格的前提下做简化. 设i为特征, 则规则1🡪2🡪…🡪i🡪…🡪n表示</p><p>若有1, 则仅显1; </p><p>若无1有2, 则仅显2; </p><p>……; </p><p>若无1~i有i+1, 则仅显i+1; </p><p>……; </p><p>若无1~n, 则全显.</p><p><strong>角 (棱). </strong>全显或全不显规则.</p><p><strong>侧面格.</strong></p><p>棒规则:   棒🡪反线🡪花灯🡪灯🡪反棒🡪花砖;</p><p>反线规则: 棒&amp;反线🡪花灯🡪灯🡪反棒🡪花砖;</p><p>花灯规则: 棒&amp;反线&amp;花灯🡪灯🡪反棒🡪花砖;</p><p>灯规则:   棒&amp;反线&amp;花灯&amp;灯🡪反棒🡪花砖;</p><p>反棒规则: 棒&amp;反线&amp;花灯&amp;灯&amp;反棒🡪花砖.</p><p>全不显规则.</p><p><strong>顶面格. </strong></p><p>是否强制显示顶面角?</p><p>棒规则: 棒🡪反棒;</p><p>反棒规则: 仅显示棒&amp;反棒;</p><p>全不显规则.</p><p><strong>2. 立体图简化 </strong>(用于&amp;stage=EO)</p><p>仅显黑黄的12个格位置:</p><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/visualcube-simplified-image-setting/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p>"},"algs":[],"thumb":"/stats/data/alg/media/visualcube-simplified-image-setting/en/image2.svg","warningCount":0,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
